id: monica-dependabot-commitlint
title: Fixed generated Dependabot commit bodies failing body line-length rules while retaining Conventional Commit subject validation
description: Dependabot commit bodies contain long generated URLs that violate body-max-line-length and fail every dependency PR.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[3]: ci,commitlint,dependabot
created_at: "2026-07-16T16:58:08.932Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-21T17:27:12.303Z"
deadline: "2026-07-18T16:58:08.932Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-16T17:19:30.466Z"
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: Dependabot commits pass; malformed Conventional Commit subjects still fail; policy is explicit in a committed config
definition_of_ready: A failed Commit Message Lint log identifies body-max-line-length as the only violation.
parent: monica-security-modernization
reviewer: unbraind
risk: medium
confidence: 100
sprint: 2026-07-security-modernization
release: next
reporter: Repository audit
severity: medium
environment: GitHub Actions pull_request commit-message job
repro_steps: Inspect run 26767553085; generated Vitest URL exceeds 100 characters.
resolution: Added committed Conventional Commit configuration that disables only body-max-line-length while preserving subject validation; CI now checks out the config before linting.
expected_result: Dependabot commit bodies pass while malformed subjects remain rejected.
actual_result: Dependabot PRs #46 through #49 passed Commit Message Lint; local negative-subject proof still rejects invalid Conventional Commit subjects.
affected_version: 2026.3.6-2
component: ci-policy
regression: false
customer_impact: Automated maintenance is blocked by a formatting-only failure.
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  monica-security-modernization,related,"2026-07-16T16:58:08.932Z",null,null
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:58:08.932Z",codex-root,The fix must not disable commit lint wholesale.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:58:08.932Z",codex-root,Add an explicit commitlint config that disables body line length only.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:58:08.932Z",codex-root,Generated URLs are not meaningfully wrappable by Dependabot; subject convention is the valuable policy.
files[1]{path,scope,note}:
  .github/workflows/ci.yml,project,commit lint job
tests[1]{command,scope,note}:
  npx commitlint --from origin/master --to HEAD,project,commit subject policy
docs[1]{path,scope,note}:
  CONTRIBUTING.md,project,commit convention
close_reason: Commit policy repaired and proven by generated bot commits
body: The commit message gate should retain Conventional Commit subject validation while allowing machine-generated dependency metadata and URLs in bodies.
